Monkey Goblin
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait
	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Monkey Goblin],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]
	PRERACE:1,Goblin
	PREREGION:1,Mediogalti
	DESC:You are adept at arboreal activity, and are more at home in the branches of a tree than you are on the ground. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Acrobatics and Climb checks while climbing trees.
	SOURCEPAGE:pg.16

Scion of Goblinblood
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait
	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Scion of Goblinblood],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]
	PRERACE:1,Goblin
	PREREGION:1,Isger
	DESC:The fury of the Goblinblood Wars still courses through your veins. Whenever you're within 60 feet of an enemy hobgoblin, you gain a +1 trait bonus on all weapon damage rolls.
	SOURCEPAGE:pg.16



